  "keyFeatures": [
    "16 plug-in persist adapters implementing the full backtest-kit IPersist* contract on PostgreSQL + Redis",
    "Atomic ON CONFLICT … DO UPDATE … RETURNING upserts — no read-then-write races under concurrent access",
    "Redis O(1) ID cache in front of every PostgreSQL context-key lookup",
    "Pgpool-II dev cluster (1 primary + 2 streaming replicas) that surfaces replication-lag bugs in development",
    "Look-ahead bias protection via a `when: Date` epoch column on all signal-affecting tables",
    "Soft-delete pattern for Measure, Interval, and Memory using server-side jsonb_set",
    "TypeORM schema auto-synchronisation — no manual migrations required",
    "Three execution modes: backtest, live, and paper trading",
    "Single docker-compose file for the full container stack with env-file configuration"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
